data.eml:eml: New taxa and notes of some described species of Agraeciini (Orthoptera: Tettigoniidae: Conocephalinae) from Malay Peninsula

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Tan, Ming Kai, Ingrisch, Sigfrid (2014): New taxa and notes of some described species of Agraeciini (Orthoptera: Tettigoniidae: Conocephalinae) from Malay Peninsula. Zootaxa 3765 (6): 541-556, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3765.6.3
